window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cole and his enslaved coven have saved Scholomance from total destruction and proven their worth. </p> <p>But things donâ€™t get easier from there. </p> <p>Scholomance and all Wicca-kind are still at war with the Elder gods, so to improve their chances of success, the Headmistress of Scholomance decides to hold an ancient, traditional tournament to strengthen their alliances with other dark academies. </p> <p>The games are bloodthirsty and deadly, but Cole and his coven are ready to face anything. </p>"; 
